PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Joshua Maurice ROBINSON, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 156463
COA: 338921 Supreme Court of Michigan. January 8, 2019

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, the motion of attorney Tracie Gittleman to extend the time for filing her Court-ordered response is GRANTED. The response will be accepted as timely filed if submitted on or before February 8, 2019.
